The paper deals with security vulnerabilities in computer systems, specifically transient execution attacks. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves evaluating defenses and implementing proof-of-concept attacks, which could fall under the categories of computer architecture (cs.AR), software engineering (cs.SE), programming languages (cs.PL), and systems and control (cs.SY).
